<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She gave birth to her son, Onyx, just four months ago.</p>

<p>And on Thursday, Iggy Azalea flaunted her incredible post-baby body in a series of pictures shared to Instagram.</p>

<p>The Australian rapper, 30, displayed her impossibly tiny waist in black corset, which clung tightly to her slender waist.</p>

<p>Post-baby body: She gave birth to her son Onyx four months ago, and on Thursday Iggy Azalea (pictured) flaunted her incredible body in a series of pictures on social media</p>

<p>In the photos, the blonde bombshell highlighted her figure in the form-fitting top, which she paired with a slinky black skirt. </p>

<p>She styled her long locks in a messy updo styled with a rockabilly head scarf.</p>

<p>Iggy looked glamorous with flawless foundation, winged eyeliner and nude lips, and accessorised with large hoop earrings. </p>

<p>Curves in all the right places: The Australian rapper showed of her tiny waist in a sultry corset which clung to her hourglass figure</p>

<p>It comes just four months after the singer welcomed her first son, Onyx.  </p>

<p>Iggy, whose real name Amethyst Amelia Kelly, confirmed via social media in June that she had become a mother.</p>

<p>She took to her Instagram Story in June to announce the news, which had been the subject of speculation since April.</p>

<p>Big news: After more than a month of rumors, Iggy Azalea has confirmed she's a mom</p>

<p>'I have a son. I kept waiting for the right time to say something but it feels like the more time passes the more I realize I'm always going to feel anxious to share news that giant with the world,' she wrote.</p>

<p>'I want to keep his life private but wanted to make it clear he is not a secret &amp; I love him beyond words.' </p>

<p>While she hasn't confirmed it, the child's father is believed to be her long-term boyfriend, rapper Playboi Carti. </p>

